{"tid":1518412,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人最近覺得抖唔到氣","createTime":"2019-08-30T08:50:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:05:41.000Z","uid":33153,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"26a4e80c6b17fcb81f0645b1014b30753bf5b4d1","tid":1518412,"uid":33153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:50:53.000Z","msg":"係真係講緊抖唔到氣<br />\n<br />\n每晚都瞓唔著 瞓著就發惡夢<br />\n每日都好早醒 心口會痛<br />\n好無精神 坐坐下突然覺得呼吸困難<br />\n好唔開心 好想喊<br />\n<br />\n呢個地方係咪仲有希望<br />\n耶穌啊我見唔到<br />\n見到盧義士個post 好肯定自己唔會死<br />\n但都唔想生存"},{"pid":"9f133add8350864447770eb568e1623986c24e95","tid":1518412,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2C0Wvub.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2C0Wvub.gif&h=e09262cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUigpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=04de2941\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUigpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=6dde7ced\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUigpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=9ade9128\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"225bf0597bbe83bffbf68455a45e9320877de7a4","tid":1518412,"uid":33153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:51:27.000Z","msg":"定我應該開喺健康台 可能開錯台 sorry"},{"pid":"10ee9e70c37472072234fef4badf6b33a031a753","tid":1518412,"uid":278377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0